    <div id="card" class="card">
        <h2>Happy Women's Day, Souptika! üéâ</h2>
        <p>Souptika, the Midnight Warrior ‚Äì your battles were never struggles, they were wars, and you have fought them bravely. Your strength, resilience, and courage inspire all. May this day be as powerful as you are!</p>
